variable {R : Type u} [CommRing R]

variable (R : Type u) [CommRing R] (M : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) R)

theorem matrix_2x2_entries_zero : M 0 1 = 0 ∧ M 1 0 = 0 :=
begin
  split,
  exact rfl,
  exact rfl,
end

variable {R : Type u} [CommRing R] (M : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) R)

theorem Matrix.zero_off_diag_entries :
  M 0 1 = 0 ∧ M 1 0 = 0 :=
begin
  split;
  refl,
end

variable {R : Type u} [CommRing R] (M : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) R)

theorem matrix_entries (h : M = ![![M 0 0, M 0 1], ![M 1 0, M 1 1]]) :
  M 0 1 = 0 ∧ M 1 0 = 0 := by
  simp [h]

variable {R : Type*} [CommRing R] (M : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) R)

theorem matrix_entries_zeros :
  M 0 1 = 0 ∧ M 1 0 = 0 := by
  simp [Matrix.zero_apply]
